      "start_time": 43.46,
      "recording_attendee_id": "97cb7ee3-4b94-4843-a15e-a525edb7c625",
      "order_number": 13,
      "text": "The reason for my call, I wanted to see if there might be an opportunity to uh I'm sorry about that uh to grab some time later this week or even after the holiday to learn a little bit more about how you guys are reaching renters. We just raised a huge round of funding and are reaching more renters than ever before. And would love to, I would love to see if we might be able to have a conversation around that and see if uh, might be an opportunity to to partner together."
