      "recording_id": "b449cb1e-99e4-402d-bb43-9d30adbe7d01",
      "end_time": 81.15,
      "start_time": 70.7,
      "recording_attendee_id": "14158e42-a883-4998-85b5-ed04d13174e4",
      "order_number": 14,
      "text": "Oh okay. Well we um, we typically don't have filling our our spaces, so um I don't know that we'd be interested in looking at it right now. Um"
    },
    {
      "id": "89c17abb-7e3f-4095-baaf-b844b1cf7e62",
      "recording_id": "b449cb1e-99e4-402d-bb43-9d30adbe7d01",
      "end_time": 88.46,
      "start_time": 81.08,
      "recording_attendee_id": "97cb7ee3-4b94-4843-a15e-a525edb7c625",
      "order_number": 15,
      "text": "Okay. Okay. Do you do you have any, I guess when you do have issues if they ever do come up, when"
    },
    {
      "id": "89c17abb-7e3f-4095-baaf-b844b1cf7e62",
      "recording_id": "b449cb1e-99e4-402d-bb43-9d30adbe7d01",
