      "id": "89c17abb-7e3f-4095-baaf-b844b1cf7e62",
      "recording_id": "b449cb1e-99e4-402d-bb43-9d30adbe7d01",
      "end_time": 106.21,
      "start_time": 94.47,
      "recording_attendee_id": "14158e42-a883-4998-85b5-ed04d13174e4",
      "order_number": 19,
      "text": "Well, I mean usually, you know, summertime is is typically a busier season, but um, I mean, I think I think all of our properties have waiting lists or courtesy list um, that they, that they draw from. So"
    },
    {
      "id": "89c17abb-7e3f-4095-baaf-b844b1cf7e62",
