      "start_time": 111.15,
      "recording_attendee_id": "97cb7ee3-4b94-4843-a15e-a525edb7c625",
      "order_number": 22,
      "text": "Yeah. Yeah that's been a lot of what I'm hearing too um I know a lot of, a lot of the people that I'm meeting with um and I'm not sure if you guys fall into this category, do you guys currently utilize any IOS to to continue that constant flow of renters coming in to fill those waiting lists or how how are you doing that?"
